{"tid":247314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MUJI無印良品20萬100呎小屋　自己蝸居自己砌","createTime":"2017-05-17T16:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T03:28:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e498183fd24db08adc36d28935f49347acf9513","tid":247314,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:34:06.000Z","msg":"12:32 2017/05/17<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1810000/1814542/muji_thumb-20170517_c_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1810000%2F1814542%2Fmuji_thumb-20170517_c_1024.jpg&h=bd38b4ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本無印良品的家品就見得多，想不到竟然也推出可以自己動手砌的小屋子，今年秋季上市。<br />\n<br />\n更多置業裝修報道【按此即睇】<br />\n<br />\nMuji Hut無印小屋室內面積為9.1平方米，即約98平方呎，另有3.1平方米（約33平方呎）平台走廊，兩小口或3至4人的小家庭都夠住有餘。但要留意小屋並無廚房廁所，有需要時或要到附近公廁或食肆解決。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1810000/1814542/hut2017_planimg03_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1810000%2F1814542%2Fhut2017_planimg03_1024.png&h=e125c262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Muji Hut無印小屋室內面積約98平方呎（Muji Hut網頁圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n無印強調，小屋適合家庭露營度假時出動，可以去到邊砌到邊，無論身處山腳、海邊，抑或公園，都可以立即砌出這間完全融入大自然的蝸居安樂窩，組件備巨型落地玻璃趟門，能夠吸收窗外自然光，符合環保概念，而全屋貫徹無印簡約自然風，木材均made in Japan，由專業工匠打造，防腐耐用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無印小屋料於今年秋季僅限日本發售，盛惠300萬日圓（約20.8萬港元），包1年保養。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1814542/MUJI%E7%84%A1%E5%8D%B0%E8%89%AF%E5%93%8120%E8%90%AC100%E5%91%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%B1%8B%E3%80%80%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E8%9D%B8%E5%B1%85%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%A0%8C?mtc=10001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1814542%2FMUJI%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%2593%258120%25E8%2590%25AC100%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B1%258B%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E8%259D%25B8%25E5%25B1%2585%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E7%25A0%258C%3Fmtc%3D10001&d=k77hOMsO7CBmOnyTOgf%2B4f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3295eee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1814542/MUJI%E7%84%A1%E5%8D%B0%E8%89%AF%E5%93%8120%E8%90%AC100%E5%91%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%B1%8B%E3%80%80%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E8%9D%B8%E5%B1%85%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%A0%8C?mtc=10001</a>"},{"pid":"d65ab230e3ee8de1ed8e1eaf079ae6855fa3da77","tid":247314,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"MUJI無印良品拆解 納米單位家具慳位大法<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1766398/MUJI_exmobile_20170410_J_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1766398%2FMUJI_exmobile_20170410_J_1024.png&h=6236feee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港納米樓愈推愈多，要令蝸居有更大空間，除了使用多用途式傢俱外，增加收納空間，亦要懂得捨棄不必要的物品，才可避免家中雜物過多。MUJI無印良品除了推出簡約風的產品外，亦有為顧客提供免費的家具收納諮詢服務，部分分店內駐有具室內設計經驗的專業家具配置顧問，幫助顧客在家中的小天地騰出空間。<br />\n<br />\nMUJI無印的其中一位專業家具配置顧問黃庭輝（Ricky），教大家一些執屋整理、家具配置的小貼士：<br />\n<br />\n1. 按使用程度決定擺放高低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1766398/tomf0331212_630_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1766398%2Ftomf0331212_630_1024.jpg&h=96875dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如圖所示，較常用的衣物，就放在正前方的水平位置，下方的則方較次要的物品；最不常用的物品如行李箱則可放在櫃頂。湯炳強攝</span><br />\n<br />\n黃庭輝建議，不同物品的擺放位置，可按使用的常用程度來決定擺放的高低。由視線水平位置至手掌向下垂時指尖高度，應擺放最常用的物品；較為次要的、或較重的物品則應放在底部，既考慮其使用頻繁程度，亦考慮了傢俱的承重能力。<br />\n<br />\n至於最少用的物品則放在高處，例如現時天氣漸轉炎熱，冬天用的棉被、厚身衣服等摺疊好後，可放在收納箱內，然後擺放在櫃頂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1766398/tomf0331226_630_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1766398%2Ftomf0331226_630_1024.jpg&h=0f09a763&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0da0081d426f20ebff8d3d5460de6fe07d70f472","tid":247314,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"2. 櫃內物品分門別類<br />\n<br />\n櫃外要擺放整齊，櫃內物品的收納分佈上亦要分門別類，井井有條。黃庭輝指，可使用一些分隔架為櫃內的物品分類，將T恤、襪子等清楚分隔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1766398/tomf0331211_630_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1766398%2Ftomf0331211_630_1024.jpg&h=c51d064a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">要分隔櫃內空間，除了使用不織布分層架外，亦可使用圖中的PV膠架將物品分門別類。湯炳強攝</span><br />\n<br />\n至於擺放次序方面，即將使用的物品可放在抽屜內最前位置，而剛洗淨的放在靠近櫃內的一方，使用時就更有規律。另外，尺寸愈小的物品，其實愈需要規範存放，否則只會變成一堆廢物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1766398/tomf0331210_630_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1766398%2Ftomf0331210_630_1024.jpg&h=42bbcd09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">櫃內的各種衣物亦要妥善分門別類，拿出來使用時就會更加方便。湯炳強攝</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 收納空間八二法則<br />\n<br />\n要騰出空間，自然亦要清理不必要的雜物。黃庭輝指，他們會建議客人只保留自己喜歡、有用的物品，令收納空間維持8成滿的狀態；至於剩餘的2成空間，則用來預留放置未來買入的物資，或家居變動之用。<br />\n<br />\n他亦指出，港人熱愛收藏整個系列的收藏品，如模型、書本等，亦令空間進一步減少。他建議，如需購置新物品，最好遵從買一件、丟一件的原則，以免出現爆棚危機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1766398/tomf0331227_630_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1766398%2Ftomf0331227_630_1024.jpg&h=88af6c20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0c2b5be83ec0a2d62c75021268e3a0d9547c0a4","tid":247314,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:40:19.000Z","msg":"4. 視乎環境選用不同物料的收納箱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一些容易受潮濕影響的物品，如紙張，特別需要小心處理。黃庭輝建議，鋅鐵箱的物料密度較高，適合用作擺放需要防潮的物品；不鏽鋼層架亦因為比木製層架適合放在廚房內使用。至於其他物料，則視乎戶主想營造一個怎樣的家具感覺，如希望家居更有現代感，可用多些不鏽鋼家具。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kJQjkBTtKsY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkJQjkBTtKsY&d=k77hOMsO7CBmOnyTOgf%2B4f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4846b962\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kJQjkBTtKsY</a><br />\n5. 「立體式」摺褲法更慳位<br />\n<br />\n一般人慣用「平摺式」的方法（即將長褲左右對摺，再上下摺疊）來摺長褲，但原來佔位較多，如改用「立體式」方法來摺，同一大小的櫃內可放更多條長褲！想學識此招摺褲新方法，立即睇片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yxB9iy8pVcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyxB9iy8pVcs&d=k77hOMsO7CBmOnyTOgf%2B4f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=286a6646\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yxB9iy8pVcs</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，目前無印良品在5間分店內為顧客免費提供家具配置諮詢服務，包括分別於銅鑼灣利舞台、太古城店、尖沙咀海港城店、奧海城店及九龍塘又一城店。市民如需使用其諮詢服務，可在其網上或店內預約。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1766398/MUJI%E7%84%A1%E5%8D%B0%E8%89%AF%E5%93%81%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%20%E7%B4%8D%E7%B1%B3%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%B7%E6%85%B3%E4%BD%8D%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95?mtc=10016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1766398%2FMUJI%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%2593%2581%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%2520%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2585%25B7%25E6%2585%25B3%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B3%2595%3Fmtc%3D10016&d=k77hOMsO7CBmOnyTOgf%2B4f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=7784c8bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1766398/MUJI%E7%84%A1%E5%8D%B0%E8%89%AF%E5%93%81%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%20%E7%B4%8D%E7%B1%B3%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%B7%E6%85%B3%E4%BD%8D%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95?mtc=10016</a>"},{"pid":"77b51b7157054d26a9cd89304761cf301c0810eb","tid":247314,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"嫌小屋太「離地」？其實無印亦曾大改造香港公屋，把一個實用面積約440呎的單位增加儲物空間：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dOv-uB2bfuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdOv-uB2bfuo&d=k77hOMsO7CBmOnyTOgf%2B4f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0fb804e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dOv-uB2bfuo</a><br />\nMUJI內政部顧問新井亨與業主了解溝通後，全屋清空進行大改造。設計師將單位重新間隔，並充分利用木櫃增加收納空間，將家中必須的物品分門別類。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1390000/1391366/muji_house_thumb_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1390000%2F1391366%2Fmuji_house_thumb_1024_1024.jpg&h=1bd2d0db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14265b0bc9457f1157da105d1be02112d068c400","tid":247314,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:01:00.000Z","msg":"上面無印裝修搞得幾好<br />\n唔知要收幾多錢？"},{"pid":"41bb83c70e52b66fdde6e0b8056281e5ad4f5f3d","tid":247314,"uid":34647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"俾得起20萬我租樓好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0902f7caaa603ce62235661f7c0118276d4d467","tid":247314,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面無印裝修搞得幾好<br />\n唔知要收幾多錢？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1375346/?r=tdsdhn&amp;lcc=at\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1375346%2F%3Fr%3Dtdsdhn%26lcc%3Dat&d=k77hOMsO7CBmOnyTOgf%2B4f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=7e6e7d99\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1375346/?r=tdsdhn&amp;lcc=at</a>"},{"pid":"55925168883dde43220b640e9dbd4df4a50d7dd5","tid":247314,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"唔好貼Topick啦"},{"pid":"861fc614d567428c62061389d8605f9943daf2cd","tid":247314,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T18:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好貼Topick啦</blockquote><br />\n點解??同政治有關??"},{"pid":"1427b32827865760606c37c80b5a4c2284d88608","tid":247314,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T19:36:09.000Z","msg":"香港可以邊到起間咁既野<br />\n農地?"},{"pid":"13fc107c69a289d0846f49dfbd795927be6c976d","tid":247314,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T23:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港可以邊到起間咁既野<br />\n農地?</blockquote><br />\n香港就算吧，全香港任何地方都係屬於政府，就算你匿埋起，畀人發現或公開咗，啲地政署就會埋嚟搵你話此土地屬於政府，然後要你短時間內拆走或罰錢。好喇，到你有錢想買呢塊地，我諗你都唔會起呢啲咁細嘅單位畀自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467a67391913f32b79812a98deab609974563220","tid":247314,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:28:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好貼Topick啦</blockquote><br />\n點解？"},{"pid":"b07c262262ba0d34783cdfe1a86c73827102f8ea","tid":247314,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:29:46.000Z","msg":"港哩真係冇尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244e7e443919ed2d0fb4348fc69fd4397a657700","tid":247314,"uid":73237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面無印裝修搞得幾好<br />\n唔知要收幾多錢？</blockquote><br />\n好似50萬<br />\n仲要廚房浴室無攪"},{"pid":"96fd59e44a5daff96e1230a7f50f825239e48f47","tid":247314,"uid":15328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上面無印裝修搞得幾好<br />\n唔知要收幾多錢？</blockquote><br />\n好似50萬<br />\n仲要廚房浴室無攪</blockquote><br />\n咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b493c16ebdec6abc7b404bd98e7acc83c99040","tid":247314,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上面無印裝修搞得幾好<br />\n唔知要收幾多錢？</blockquote><br />\n好似50萬<br />\n仲要廚房浴室無攪</blockquote><br />\n咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n儲少d廢物就唔使咁多儲物空間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1437173da5f4ddacd517b70631ffbd21c178d01","tid":247314,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0